[dog panting]
[groans]

00:06:26.807 --> 00:06:28.109
Huh?

00:06:29.879 --> 00:06:31.716
[SHIZUKA groans]

00:06:33.320 --> 00:06:34.923
Morning, Roo.
[dog yapping]

00:06:34.956 --> 00:06:38.162
Are you feeling better?

00:06:38.195 --> 00:06:41.937
Oh, thank...
Thank goodness.

00:06:41.971 --> 00:06:42.905
